{
  "name": "RPlog_An_Unscrupulous_Undertaking_Deal_With_the_Devil",
  "title": "An Unscrupulous Undertaking: Deal With the Devil",
  "summary": "In a gambling hall, the unsettling agent Elias materializes at the elbow of the mercenary Nastaran Zohreh, needling her with refined menace until she whirls and throws whiskey in his face. Unfazed, Elias dabs himself clean and reveals he is paralyzed from the waist down by a severed spine, gliding in a hover-chair as he lays out an offer from his shadowy employers: piloting a shipment that, he eventually admits, will contain enslaved Wookiees. Nastaran recoils at the word \"slaves\" and at Elias's dodgy evasions, but he hooks her with something far more personal -- a woman who \"looks just like her\" and who could make a full recovery with the right care, leverage that drains the color from Nastaran's face. Shaken and furious, she demands to know why she was singled out and who he serves, but Elias only smiles like a nightmarish apparition and presses a credit chip into her unwilling hand. Nastaran pockets the chip while insisting she has made no decision at all, even as the devil's bargain closes around her.",
